a few things from my first time there:

• Food is very cheap. I ate double portions at every meal. Whoops lol.

• I lived through a Cat 4 hurricane. Meow.

• Dec/Jan is the best whale szn.

• Speed bumps are everywhere and they’re massive.

• Everyone drives crazy and no one has road rage.

also, if you hate lizards don’t slide lol.

Get you friends that hear you and pray for you 🙏🏾

@icmerz and I were just talking at Bryant park at 11pm and after hearing each other we just decided to pray for one another 

I won’t get into the details but I do want to remind you that the Bible says a friend is always loyal and a brother is born to help in a time of need 

Proverbs 17:17 

Don’t neglect the power of praying in the midst of your everyday life. And it doesn’t have to be the perfect time, you don’t need to bun candles or even have worship music playing you just need to talk to God

@psychobunny / summer ‘22

blessed is an understatement.

“But God my dream is to do that, why do you have me doing this?” - everyone

What if what you’re doing now is a stepping stone to get you to where God has you AND your dream.

He gave you those dreams for a reason.

Trust the God. 
Trust the process. 

❤️

Sometimes we forget that in the tough times, God is still good. It never changes. Don’t let your situation change your perspective.

*someone screams in the back*
“God is good all the time and all the time God is good”
😂😂😂

Ecc. 7:14

Camping 🏕️🎣

Went camping last week and man was it the best 4 days. No service. BBQ everything. #gonefishing (but apparently the fish are smarter than me) Caught up in my book. God’s beauty literally every direction. Old friends. Stillness. The best time.

a week with pops + a new toy 🐎

Ever since I was in middle school, we’ve been talking about this car. It’s been a long time coming and a lot of “when are we gonna get that mustang out of the shed and start working on it” He has this week off from work & I made sure to grab it 😂

The plan is to restore this ‘66 mustang together. I can already see his wheels spinning on what to do and what to buy 😂 
Doing the car will be great, but I’m more so looking forward to the journey doing it.
